{"tid":1867904,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"你地第一日返工會點融入公司同事上司?","createTime":"2020-02-07T10:42:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-11T18:03:32.000Z","uid":343020,"like":6,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"ec575af5af1a661497226a5054ecc1440f1138ce","tid":1867904,"uid":343020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T10:42:09.000Z","msg":"<strong><ins>第一日返新工要注意啲咩?5招助你快速攻心!點俾上司同事好印象?</ins></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/EKPxIUReASY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FEKPxIUReASY&d=uFnVTFPFhHj2sSFH0VdWwVKEWDR5zjN73Co06CeqttY%3D&h=d20b448c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/EKPxIUReASY</a><br />\n<br />\n我進入一間新公司時,快速融入公司既5式,大家又有咩心得分享?<br />\n<br />\n自問唔係專家，只係一些透過個人經驗不斷學習翻黎的心得和分享<br />\n我既目標係希望盡量幫香港人可以搜集一些免費實用/含經濟效益/搵到食既資料<br />\n計劃黎緊主要會上載既片/資源題材包括<br />\n<br />\n求職/轉工<br />\n職業發展<br />\n進修〔搵下有冇啲可以幫大家有一技之長/移民(唔係冇選擇都唔鼓勵)加分既知識〕<br />\n其他實用野等等...稔到再整<br />\n<br />\n大家如果係搵工／進修上面有咩疑難都可以盡量係到問，我答到盡力答<br />\n<br />\n 其他參考:<br />\n面試難題拆解「你點解想轉工？」5個漂亮理由和一堆忌諱理由大分享!<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/2pSEsXhauQk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F2pSEsXhauQk&d=uFnVTFPFhHj2sSFH0VdWwVKEWDR5zjN73Co06CeqttY%3D&h=20a430f2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/2pSEsXhauQk</a>"},{"pid":"12932e86fd057a8cf03531f124722627a8a317b6","tid":1867904,"uid":249475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T12:01:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c5e145aaa97b7d133d9a7fe7c6715b2d3edbc08","tid":1867904,"uid":199716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T15:24:17.000Z","msg":"Fuck u"},{"pid":"f7cfbce3770f1d706059404174fa64ba7f7d1c59","tid":1867904,"uid":169845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T16:24:16.000Z","msg":"Lm <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\